long_desc.thetext:
Right now we have the problem that select boxes are sometimes not shown right (when clicked on a select box, nothing happens) or after displaying select boxes the view is broken. This seems to be a problem for both OS, Android and iOS. We should implement an own select box:
* On click on a select box we should display a popup with a list inside, that is looking like the native once * When an item is selected the popup is closed and the value is set on the original select box

Realized a select box, by creating a dialog including a list with model values.
Fixed with: a1e249b9de7623527c0dd7a68673cdfe5ee406d5
Created attachment 1131 Screenshot of new select box for qooxdoo mobile
*** Bug 5498 has been marked as a duplicate of this bug. ***

Review: - Refactored some methods - Added selection feature
Please add * a tick instead of a selection * please redesign the selectbox -> should be more visible

Native selectbox and different appearance (text) does not work with firefox. See: https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=649849
That is why, we just use a Input Type="Text", and no select box, because this can be styled in needed design.
* Use Container Element instead of content element (because it is the same) * Use _setAttribute instead of qx.bom.element.Attribute.set for the container element
Closed all bugs already shipped with a release.
